    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Thank you for printing Lou Cannon's article. I would like to clarify, however, that although I met with him and spoke to him on the phone several times, I did not relay to him the contents of any of my conversations with Javier Ovando, as I was still bound by the attorney-client privilege.</p>
        <p>Tamar Toister  Deputy Public Defender  Los Angeles</p>
      </block>
